Ranger Help for: sharpen
========================

SYNTAX:      sharpen <weapon>
             edge <weapon>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     35
SKILL TYPE:  survival

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to sharpen a bladed weapon using a rock,
improving its damage temporarily. The Ranger must have a rock in their
inventory. Only slash and pierce weapons can be sharpened. The
effectiveness depends on the Ranger's training, and the keen edge
persists for a meaningful stretch of time before it dulls again.
The 'edge' command is an alias for 'sharpen'.

If you are in hills, mountains, or underground terrain, you can use
'quarry' to gather a suitable rock first.
